=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Tutorials_06-Presented-in-Living-Stereo_ex6 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright clean sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 54 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and percussive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: percussive
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 53.8246
  harmonic_decay_rate: -1.8621
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9230
  pitch_clarity: 4.5506
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -9.6157
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
